GGn RANKING UP: A PRACTICAL GUIDE
by waiter7
════════════════════════════════════

Rankings are driven by six achievement categories. Your total points across all six determine your level. Most of the path to Legendary Gamer can be covered with just a few focused habits started early on.


THE SIX STATS
- Attack (Upload GB)
- Defense (Download GB)
- Strength (Torrents uploaded)
- Accuracy (Snatches seeded 30+ days)
- Mining (IRC lines)
- Wood Cutting (Forum posts)

You don't need to max every stat -- just accumulate enough total points across them. Focus on your strengths and let the harder ones come naturally.


── STEP 1: SMASH YOUR ACCURACY STAT (DAY ONE) ──────────────────────

The single most repeated tip in the community: snatch 2,000-2,500 tiny torrents and seed them for at least 30 days. This rockets your Accuracy points and gives you a huge head start.

Use small-filesize content so your ratio stays healthy. Best targets:

- Atari 2600 / C64 ROMs (often just a few KB each)
- TTRPG books (D&D, Pathfinder -- tons of small files)
- Other retro ROM collections

Once you hit Gamer class, the mass downloader unlocks, making it easy to grab hundreds at once. Start manually if you're not there yet -- every snatch counts.


── STEP 2: BUILD DEFENSE WITH FREELEECH ────────────────────────────

Download GB (Defense) is easiest to stack via freeleech. Several ways to get it:

Daily low-seed FL pots -- on the homepage every day. Grab these without fail. They also generate gold while you seed them.

24hr Personal Global FL -- costs ~13,500 gold from the shop. Effectively makes the whole site free for a day. Use it to pull large collections.

Global Freeleech events -- happen roughly every few months, often around holidays. When one hits, drop everything and download the largest torrents you can find. Members regularly hit 4TB+ in a single event.

Neutral leech torrents -- certain collections (large retro packs, PS3 collections, etc.) never count against your ratio. Great for long-term seeding with no risk.

Seed everything for as long as possible. Long-term seeding earns gold passively, which you reinvest into more FL tokens and upload potions.


── STEP 3: HANDLE YOUR UPLOAD (ATTACK + STRENGTH) ──────────────────

Upload is the hardest stat on a home connection. Strategies in order of effort:

Upload potions -- buy from the shop for ~9,000 gold each, adding 20GB of upload credit instantly. Not a substitute for real seeding, but bridges the gap while your ratio builds. I have a ton of these -- send me junk and I'll send you upload potions!

Seed popular/new torrents -- seeding in-demand content long-term earns upload passively over time. New releases and popular games pay off the most.

Actually upload content -- contributing new game releases to the site is one of the fastest ways to boost both Attack and Strength. Cross-seeding releases from other trackers is a well-regarded approach.

Seedbox -- if you're serious about breaking through the upload wall, a seedbox runs 24/7 at high speeds and makes a dramatic difference. Heavily credited by many members at Master Gamer and above.


── STEP 4: COMMUNITY STATS ARE FREE POINTS ─────────────────────────

IRC and forums cover two full achievement categories and cost nothing but time. Don't leave these on the table.

IRC (Mining):
Just hang out and chat. Ask questions about items, pets, trades, or whatever you're curious about -- the community is welcoming. Lines add up fast when you're genuinely engaged. You also need 2,500 lines before certain crafting items unlock, so start early. New members who mention they're new often get gold gifted to them too.

Forums (Wood Cutting):
Post in Forum Games, reply to threads, ask questions. Aiming for ~25 posts a day is very manageable. The early tiers are easy -- don't save this for later.

Gold Gloves:
Get these from the shop as soon as you can. They increase the gold you earn from seeding, which compounds everything else.


── THE FAST PATH: SUMMARY ──────────────────────────────────────────

1. Immediately start snatching small torrents -- target 2,000+ seeded for 30+ days (Accuracy)
2. Grab the daily low-seed FL pots from the homepage every single day without fail (Defense + gold)
3. Join IRC and start chatting -- lines come naturally when you're genuinely engaged (Mining)
4. Post on forums regularly; Forum Games are easy low-effort points (Wood Cutting)
5. Save gold → buy 24hr FL buffs or upload potions strategically (Attack/Defense)
6. When global FL hits, go big on large torrents, then seed them indefinitely


── BEYOND LEGENDARY: MASTER GAMER AND UP ───────────────────────────

To push past Legendary into Master Gamer and beyond, you need meaningful upload stats. That means seeding popular content heavily over time, uploading new releases to the site, or running a seedbox. The community and download stats largely take care of themselves if you stay active -- upload is the real gate.

